**What's on it:** Two plots — class distribution and age analysis.

**What to say (20 sec):**
> "Our EDA revealed several key patterns. The class distribution plot on the left confirms the extreme imbalance. On the right, we see that malignant lesions are more frequent in older patients — age is a discriminative feature. We also found differential prevalence across anatomical sites and sexes, and several TBP colour features showed strong discriminative power."

