**What to say (30 sec):**
> "Why does tabular dominate? The 3D-TBP metadata already encodes colour, size, and border statistics in numerical form — exactly what gradient-boosted trees excel at. Feature engineering captured non-linear and per-patient relationships.
>
> Key lesson from Phase 2: 393 positives are insufficient for CNN training at 1:1,020 imbalance, even with Focal Loss, MixUp, and subsampling. However, the pipeline infrastructure — CV alignment, HDF5 loading, late fusion — is fully built and ready for future improvements with more data."

